urlText: Trackwork may affect your travel
content:
Saturday 23 and Sunday 24 October
  • All Cronulla and some Waterfall trains make extra stops at St Peters and Erskineville.
  • Daily between 8am and 8pm, extra trains run between Hurstville and Bondi Junction.
  • On Sunday from 12.50am until 4.40am, buses replace most trains between Hurstville and Central.
  • Some trains continue to run from Central to Cronulla or Waterfall, to a changed timetable.
  • Trains run between Bondi Junction and Central only.
  • Plan your trip before you travel for up-to-date information.
Bus route
3AT4: Hurstville then express to Central and return
7T4: Hurstville all stations to Sydenham, then Central and return
subtitle: Trackwork may affect your travel
